name: Tales Of Momotaro
description:
Tales Of Momotaro were inspired by Japanese Folklore titled Momotaro, which is sounds so familiar in almost everyone childhood.
The main idea itself is to encourage every adult to take a break for a while then give themself a throwback to remind about any of Momotaro folklore moral value, such as an optimistic character and the bold mentality to face any kind of his adventure challenges.
And why is it important for me to representated Momotaro folklore into a mature audiences? Cause i believe that every adult still need a good imaginative side that contained a bravery and optimistic self to face their hard time.
